I have called McDonalds to complain. They never do anything usually for complaints. Let's see.
poor product and service

Suspecting way too many people just there (or around there) for WiFi so it basically doesn’t work even if you are a paid customer.

Too crowded

reviews.text: 食物新鮮
平通街種類多服務高是一間真正為市民服務的快餐店。
呢間老麥優點唔駛等太耐，缺點係超細間唔好咁多幻想空間，外賣好走。
桌子比較污糟，常常爆滿人，只得一部自助售票機
這裏沒有令我討厭的地方坐得很舒服
